display="inline"><![CDATA[I = {\mathopen {}\left \{a\right \}\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex>. Conversely, assume that each element is the supremum of its positive part and fix a semidirected subset <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[I\subseteq  A]]></fr:tex>. We compute:</fr:p>

  <fr:tex
display="block"><![CDATA[\bigsqcup {\mathopen {}\left \{a \in  I \mid  \mathsf {pos}\,a\right \}\mathclose {}}   =   \bigsqcup _{a\in  {\mathopen {}\left \{a \in  I\mid  \mathsf {pos}\,a\right \}\mathclose {}}}a   =   \bigsqcup _{a\in  I}\bigsqcup _{p\in  \mathsf {pos}\,a} a   =   \bigsqcup _{a\in  I} a   ]]></fr:tex>
